<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.1">
<l>kalaiyuṅ kariyum parimāvun</l>
<l>tiriyuṅ kāṉaṅ kaṭantupōy</l>
<l>cilaiyuṅ kaṇaiyun tuṇaiyākac</l>
<l>ceṉṟāṉ veṉṟic ceṟukkaḷattu,</l>
<l>malaikoṇ ṭalainī raṇaikaṭṭi</l>
<l>matiḷnī rilaṅkai vāḷarakkar</l>
<l>talaivaṉ talaipat taṟuttukantāṉ</l>
<l>cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge at Śālagrāma of him who rejoiced</l>
<l rend="indent">on the victorious battlefield,</l>
<l>Cutting the ten heads of the headman of the sword[-bearing] demons</l>
<l rend="indent">of sea-walled Lanka,</l>
<l>Having taken hillocks, building a dam for the crashing waters,</l>
<l>The one who went with a bow and arrows as companions,</l>
<l rend="indent">going through the forest where stags, elephants, and horses wandered.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
